The paper deals with a computer vision problem of predicting attributes from face images, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper experiments with two large datasets, which could also place it under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
